                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-288" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL GUMMER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 131.) I apprehended the prisoner on the Thursday night after this—he denied all knowledge of it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> Going through the park, I met some boys with a jacket—they asked me to go with them; I did—they asked me if I would ask this boy whether he wanted to buy a jacket; I did so, and the boy that had the jacket gave it him—he gave me the money, and I gave it to the boy; I did not know it was stolen.</p>
